* Iron Raptor was more then surprised as Angel Prime had walked up to her, 
pleaced something in her hands then then told her to look after it for a 
while. Then, without a second thought he left.*

" What's this?"

* She more or less spoke to herself but loud enough for anyone else to hear. 
Just what was she supposed to do woth it?
Iron Raptor wasn't really a Maximal, just her programming, so she had no 
clue at just what Angel Prime had dumped into her hands before disappearing.
But then suddenly Liono caught her attention and she simply kept her hands 
around whatever this thing was. Though from Liono's tome he almost seemed to 
be mocking her and her authority. Even though he had been her commander 
before she didn't like him judging her worthyness to the commanding 
position.
Iron Raptor looked Liono over before looking him straight in the face, her 
voice just as low but with a firm grip to it.*

" I'm not opening jack squat until I know what's happening with that 
Alliance."

* This was no time to give in at anyone until she knew what was going on.*

" There's a cease fire here and the longer it goes on the longer I'm keeping 
the CF on Lock Down. Understand?"

* Iron Raptor then leaned back and looked over her shoulder at the 
murrmering voices of the Maximals.*

" Hopefully the Alliance will get in gear so we can get this over and done 
with. We have more important things to do then waste our time with this, but 
we have to wait unless we want the CF to look like the Ark."

* She narrowed her eyes and looked towards Prowl, mainly because he was the 
closest one to her. < Who's still firing?>*
